{"tid":2510562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府：前政助宣誓後以回新加坡為由請辭 已建議其應留港工作 避免引起公眾負面觀感","createTime":"2021-04-30T08:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T18:34:49.000Z","uid":21470,"like":34,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"e11186c0feec120d2472e585745d372d648b0800","tid":2510562,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:49:18.000Z","msg":"前民政局政治助理將任港台主持<br />\n<br />\n今年年初請辭的前民政事務局政治助理黎穎瑜，將轉任香港電台主持。前任行政長官及政治委任官員離職後工作諮詢委員會宣布，批准黎穎瑜擔任3份工作，包括港台節目主持、為中華國術總會撰寫功夫書籍，及擔任音樂兒童基金會項目顧問。<br />\n<br />\n44歲的黎穎瑜去年12月宣誓擁護《基本法》和效忠特區，一個月後以照顧家人為由請辭。她當時在社交網站透露，因為丈夫回流新加坡，她決定跟隨照顧年幼兒子。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389613&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=6724af43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389613</a><br />\n<br />\n前任政治委任官員黎穎瑜離職後工作<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  前任行政長官及政治委任官員離職後工作諮詢委員會（諮詢委員會）就前任民政事務局局長政治助理黎穎瑜在二○二一年一月二十日離開政府後擬擔任的工作<span class=\"gold\">給予意見</span>。<br />\n<br />\n  諮詢委員會認為在黎穎瑜遵循委員會所建議的若干規限的前提下，離職後擬擔任的工作不會構成任何潛在的利益衝突。諮詢委員會亦不預期有關工作會<span class=\"gold\">引起負面公眾觀感</span>。<br />\n <br />\n  諮詢委員會就前任政治委任官員離職後的工作或委任安排作出考慮並提供意見。在考慮每宗個案時，諮詢委員會均會參考有關前任政治委任官員所提供的資料、相關政策局或辦公室的評估，以及政治委任官員離職後工作指引所訂明的提供意見標準。<br />\n<br />\n  以上個案的詳情已列載於諮詢委員會的網站（<a href=\"http://www.ceo.gov.hk/poo/chi/index.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceo.gov.hk%2Fpoo%2Fchi%2Findex.htm&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=c4f6361a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.ceo.gov.hk/poo/chi/index.htm</a>）。<br />\n<br />\n  諮詢委員會的成員包括：<br />\n<br />\n廖柏偉教授（主席）<br />\n趙麗娟<br />\n葉錫安<br />\n梁高美懿<br />\n施文信<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2021年4月30日（星期五）<br />\n香港時間16時00分"},{"pid":"0667868205cd6c2679f1b29e74a8231c06741cc3","tid":2510562,"uid":127575,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:58:34.000Z","msg":"又唔俾人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3a80a6e6cfe9480e55368699a01d5890ca44d0","tid":2510562,"uid":276273,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"8月1，第一個被鎖港人士"},{"pid":"d3e78762f7ab8facb3bfb12b595f9df5f647ac87","tid":2510562,"uid":85629,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:00:14.000Z","msg":"辭職走人都唔俾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a4383843cc9b7d7e68447e78cc47b66a3f38c6","tid":2510562,"uid":47674,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d3e78762f7ab8facb3bfb12b595f9df5f647ac87","tid":2510562,"uid":85629,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:00:14.000Z","msg":"辭職走人都唔俾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:10:05.000Z","msg":"係家庭團聚都唔畀"},{"pid":"426833dbc8a4745e9376c12dbb2da448acee20c9","tid":2510562,"uid":291750,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"佢走唔到啦"},{"pid":"61f44d88981aa770afd5aebd3fcec8894f442c41","tid":2510562,"uid":153781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"Rap <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f3453f947b81e7ebd785b809b60faaf945d6a9","tid":2510562,"uid":6942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:17:34.000Z","msg":"酒唔到啦！"},{"pid":"7f81883bc50e7e1f00cabcd59c65c5140d4239f1","tid":2510562,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:18:36.000Z","msg":"熱廚房真係夠晒熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ec41a161f7e0fdafc45376d0158ad4c57f780c","tid":2510562,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:23:44.000Z","msg":"走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin